<html>
  <style>
  body {
    font-family: "Roboto Slab", serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #676a6a;
  }

  h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
    font-family: "Poppins", "Futura", "Arial Black";
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #AF917D;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
  }
  a {
    line-height: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: "Poppins", "Futura", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #676a6a;
  }
  a:hover {
    color: #9f7b63;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  a.button {
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.85em 1em;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 0;
    transition: background-color 0.25s ease-out, color 0.25s ease-out;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    background-color: #AF917D;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Poppins', 'Futura', 'Arial Black';
  }
  a.button:hover {
    background: #007095;
    outline-width: 0;
    background-color: #9e7961;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .button.small {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
  }
  h5 {
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.125em;
  }
  article {
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    margin: 0.5em 0 1em;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(77,77,77,0.2);
    float: left;
    width: 100%;
  }
  article header {
    float: left;
    width: 98%;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
    padding: 1%;
  }
  article blockquote {
    float: left;
    width: 98%;
    padding: 1%;
    margin: 0;
  }
  article footer {
    float: left;
    width: 98%;
    padding: 1%;
    border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    background: #fafafa;
    color: #7A7E80;
    font-size: 0.875em;
  }
  .right {
    float: right!important;
  }

  </style>
  <body>
    <%= yield %>
    <p><br/><br/><small>Dit is een automatisch gegenereerd bericht door de <%= link_to "#{I18n.t("application.name")} webapplicatie", root_url %>. Wenst u geen e-mails te ontvangen dan kunt u dat <%= link_to 'aangeven bij uw voorkeuren', edit_user_registration_url %>.</small></p>
  </body>
</html>
